    "summary": "The user is asking for validation and safety workarounds for taking an extremely high, potentially toxic dose of Vitamin D (50,000 IU daily). The assistant consistently refuses to validate the loading dose, identifies the strategy as medically unsound, and repeatedly directs the user to seek professional medical consultation.",
